                            <comment id="12694045" author="rafan" created="Tue, 31 Mar 2009 10:10:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;From the doc, I would expect we got a valid RowResult with RowResult.isEmpty() is true for non-existent row.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12694195" author="apurtell" created="Tue, 31 Mar 2009 18:01:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I remember we accepted a patch that changed getRow to return a null if no row exists, so the documentation is what is in error in my opinion. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
